<LegalLayout
  title="Website Privacy Policy — Aramo"
  description="How the Aramo website handles the limited information it collects: server logs and correspondence. No cookies, no analytics, no ad tech, no selling of personal information."
  heading="Website Privacy Policy"
>
  <h2>Who we are</h2>
  <p>
    Aramo is a product of Astre Consulting Services Inc. If you have a question
    about this policy, write to us at <a href="mailto:hello@aramo.ai"
      >hello@aramo.ai</a
    >.
  </p>

  <h2>What this policy covers</h2>
  <p>
    This policy is about this website, aramo.ai. Candidate and client data
    handled inside the Aramo platform is covered separately by our
    <a href="/legal/platform-privacy">Platform &amp; Candidate-Data Privacy
      Notice</a
    >.
  </p>

  <h2>What we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Server logs.</strong> When you visit, our servers record standard
      technical information — your IP address, your browser’s user agent, and the
      request line (the page requested and the time). We use it to keep the site
      secure and running.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Correspondence.</strong> If you email us, we keep your message and
      contact details so we can reply and keep a record of the exchange.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What we don’t do</h2>
  <p>
    This site sets <strong>no cookies</strong>. It runs no analytics, no
    advertising or tracking technology, and embeds no third-party trackers. We do
    not sell or share your personal information — ever.
  </p>

  <h2>How long we keep it</h2>
  <p>
    We keep server logs for [30 days — PO/counsel] and then delete them. We keep
    correspondence for as long as we need it to handle your request and maintain
    our records.
  </p>

  <h2>Your rights and choices</h2>
  <p>
    You can write to <a href="mailto:hello@aramo.ai">hello@aramo.ai</a> to ask
    what we hold about you, to correct it, or to ask us to delete it, subject to
    applicable law.
  </p>

  <h2>Platform data</h2>
  <p>
    If you are a candidate or a client of a staffing firm that uses Aramo, the
    data handled inside the platform is governed by our
    <a href="/legal/platform-privacy">Platform &amp; Candidate-Data Privacy
      Notice</a
    >, not this website policy.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes</h2>
  <p>
    If we change this policy, we will update this page and the version line
    below.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions about privacy? Write to <a href="mailto:hello@aramo.ai"
      >hello@aramo.ai</a
    >.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
